<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SELENE CREATORS | クリエイターと、ブランドをつなぐ。</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Zen+Kaku+Gothic+New:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Shippori+Mincho:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #faf9f7;
    --bg-card: #ffffff;
    --bg-warm: #f3f0eb;
    --accent: #9a7e5a;
    --accent-light: #b8a07a;
    --accent-warm: #c4a87c;
    --text-primary: #2c2824;
    --text-body: #4a4440;
    --text-muted: #8a847e;
    --border: rgba(154, 126, 90, 0.15);
    --border-accent: rgba(154, 126, 90, 0.3);
    --ff-display: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    --ff-jp-serif: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    --ff-body: 'Zen Kaku Gothic New', sans-serif;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--ff-body);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.9;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .container { max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 28px; }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

  .rv {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(36px);
    transition: opacity 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1),
                transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
  }
  .rv.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .rv-d1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
  .rv-d2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
  .rv-d3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }

  /* ═══ PLACEHOLDER IMAGE ═══ */
  .ph-img-box {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--ff-display);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ═══ HERO ═══ */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px 56px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--ff-display);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.45em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-accent);
    padding: 9px 28px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    display: inline-block;
    align-self: flex-start;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroFade 1s 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--ff-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroFade 1s 0.5s forwards;
  }
  .hero-title i { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 400; }

  .hero-catch {
    font-family: var(--ff-jp-serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(0.88rem, 1.6vw, 1.02rem);
    color: var(--text-body);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    line-height: 2;
    margin-top: 28px;
    max-width: 420px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroFade 1s 0.7s forwards;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 44px;
    align-self: flex-start;
    font-family: var(--ff-body);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: #fff;
    background: var(--accent);
    padding: 17px 48px;
    transition: all 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroFade 1s 0.9s forwards;
  }
  .hero-cta:hover { background: var(--accent-warm); transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(154,126,90,0.2); }
  .hero-cta svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; transition: transform 0.35s; }
  .hero-cta:hover svg { transform: translateX(5px); }

  .hero-photo { position: relative; }
  .hero-photo .ph-img-box {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4c4ac, #baa88c);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  @keyframes heroFade {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .hr { height: 1px; background: var(--border); max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto; }
  section { padding: 120px 0; }

  .sec-label {
    font-family: var(--ff-display);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .sec-title {
    font-family: var(--ff-jp-serif);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: clamp(1.45rem, 3.2vw, 2.2rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .sec-lead {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 2.05;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ═══ PHOTO STRIP ═══ */
  .photo-strip {
    width: 100%;
    height: 360px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .photo-strip .ph-img-box { height: 100%; }

  /* ═══ PROBLEM ═══ */
  .prob-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    margin-top: 64px;
  }
  .prob-col-title {
    font-family: var(--ff-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    padding-bottom: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .prob-row { display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 22px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .prob-num {
    flex-shrink: 0; font-family: var(--ff-display); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--accent);
    width: 26px; height: 26px; border: 1px solid var(--border-accent); border-radius: 50%;
    display: grid; place-items: center; margin-top: 3px; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .prob-text { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-body); line-height: 1.75; font-weight: 400; }

  /* ═══ STRENGTH ═══ */
  .sec-warm { background: var(--bg-warm); }

  .str-layout { margin-top: 64px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: start; }
  .str-diagram {
    background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 44px 36px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }
  .str-flow-step { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .str-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .str-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }
  .str-flow-label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-primary); white-space: nowrap; font-weight: 500; }
  .str-arrow { text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 2.2; user-select: none; }
  .str-result-box { background: rgba(154,126,90,0.08); border: 1px solid var(--border-accent); padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; }
  .str-result-box p { font-family: var(--ff-jp-serif); font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .str-points { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 36px; }
  .str-pt { padding-left: 22px; border-left: 2px solid var(--border); transition: border-color 0.4s; }
  .str-pt:hover { border-left-color: var(--accent); }
  .str-pt h4 { font-family: var(--ff-display); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .str-pt p { font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--text-body); line-height: 1.9; font-weight: 400; }

  /* ═══ SERVICE ═══ */
  .svc-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 64px; }
  .svc {
    background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
  }
  .svc::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent), transparent); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.45s; z-index: 2;
  }
  .svc:hover { border-color: var(--border-accent); transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .svc:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .svc-img-wrap { overflow: hidden; height: 180px; }
  .svc-img-wrap .ph-img-box { height: 100%; transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1); }
  .svc:hover .svc-img-wrap .ph-img-box { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .svc-body { padding: 28px 30px 36px; }
  .svc-num { font-family: var(--ff-display); font-size: 2.6rem; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(154,126,90,0.2); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .svc h3 { font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .svc p { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--text-body); line-height: 1.9; font-weight: 400; }

  /* ═══ FLOW ═══ */
  .flow-tl { margin-top: 64px; padding-left: 44px; position: relative; }
  .flow-tl::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 10px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 1px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), var(--border) 80%, transparent); }
  .flow-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 44px; }
  .flow-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: -38px; top: 7px; width: 9px; height: 9px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; }
  .flow-item h4 { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .flow-item h4 span { font-family: var(--ff-display); color: var(--accent); margin-right: 12px; font-weight: 500; font-size: 1rem; }
  .flow-item p { font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--text-body); line-height: 1.9; font-weight: 400; }

  /* ═══ SPLIT VISUAL ═══ */
  .split-vis { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; min-height: 400px; overflow: hidden; }
  .split-vis-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 64px 56px; background: var(--bg-warm); }
  .split-vis-text h2 { font-family: var(--ff-jp-serif); font-weight: 600; font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.4vw, 1.6rem); line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .split-vis-text p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-body); line-height: 2; font-weight: 400; }
  .split-vis-photo { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .split-vis-photo .ph-img-box { position: absolute; inset: 0; }

  /* ═══ PRICING ═══ */
  .price-box { margin-top: 64px; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.04); }
  .price-left { padding: 48px 44px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .price-left h3 { font-family: var(--ff-display); font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .price-left h3 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
  .price-left p { font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--text-body); line-height: 1.9; font-weight: 400; }
  .price-right { padding: 48px 44px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; justify-content: center; }
  .price-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; padding-bottom: 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(154,126,90,0.08); }
  .price-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
  .price-label { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--text-body); font-weight: 500; }
  .price-value { font-family: var(--ff-display); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
  .price-note { font-size: 0.76rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; font-weight: 400; }

  /* ═══ CTA ═══ */
  .cta-section { position: relative; overflow: hidden; height: 520px; }
  .cta-section .ph-img-box { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; }
  .cta-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 1;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
    padding: 40px 28px;
  }
  .cta-heading { font-family: var(--ff-jp-serif); font-weight: 600; font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.8vw, 1.9rem); color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .cta-sub { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-body); margin-bottom: 48px; font-weight: 400; }
  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: #fff; background: var(--accent); padding: 18px 56px;
    transition: all 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
  }
  .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--accent-warm); transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(154,126,90,0.2); }
  .cta-btn svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; transition: transform 0.35s; }
  .cta-btn:hover svg { transform: translateX(5px); }

  /* ═══ FOOTER ═══ */
  footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 44px 28px 28px; text-align: center; background: var(--bg-warm); }
  .ft-brand { font-family: var(--ff-display); font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 18px; font-weight: 500; }
  .ft-nav { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .ft-nav a { font-size: 0.74rem; color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.06em; transition: color 0.3s; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 400; }
  .ft-nav a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .ft-copy { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }

  /* ═══ MODAL ═══ */
  .modal-bg { display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); z-index: 10000; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 20px; }
  .modal-bg.on { display: flex; }
  .modal-box { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); max-width: 660px; width: 100%; max-height: 82vh; overflow-y: auto; padding: 48px; position: relative; box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); }
  .modal-box h2 { font-family: var(--ff-jp-serif); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
  .modal-box h3 { font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .modal-box p, .modal-box li { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-body); line-height: 1.9; font-weight: 400; }
  .modal-box ul { padding-left: 18px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .modal-box table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 14px 0; font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .modal-box th, .modal-box td { text-align: left; padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(154,126,90,0.08); vertical-align: top; }
  .modal-box th { color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 500; width: 34%; }
  .modal-box td { color: var(--text-body); font-weight: 400; }
  .modal-x { position: absolute; top: 18px; right: 18px; background: none; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-muted); width: 34px; height: 34px; cursor: pointer; display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 1rem; transition: all 0.3s; }
  .modal-x:hover { color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .ph-text { background: rgba(154,126,90,0.06); border-left: 2px solid var(--accent); padding: 7px 12px; font-size: 0.74rem; color: var(--accent); margin: 3px 0; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.6; display: block; font-weight: 400; }

  /* ═══ RESPONSIVE ═══ */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section { padding: 80px 0; }
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .hero-text { padding: 80px 28px 60px; }
    .hero-photo { height: 320px; }
    .prob-grid, .str-layout, .price-box { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .svc-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; }
    .svc-img-wrap { height: 160px; }
    .svc-body { padding: 24px 24px 30px; }
    .price-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .price-left, .price-right { padding: 36px 28px; }
    .modal-box { padding: 32px 22px; }
    .flow-tl { padding-left: 34px; }
    .ft-nav { gap: 18px; }
    .split-vis { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .split-vis-text { padding: 48px 28px; }
    .split-vis-photo { height: 260px; }
    .photo-strip { height: 240px; }
    .cta-section { height: 400px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Creator Community &amp; Matching</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">SELENE<br><i>CREATORS</i></h1>
    <p class="hero-catch">あなたのブランドに合うクリエイターを、ここから。<br>美容・ライフスタイル領域に特化した<br>クリエイターコミュニティ。</p>
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/selene.official.japan?igsh=b3J5Nmx5aWV4azVh&utm_source=qr" class="hero-cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      お問い合わせ
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-photo">
    <!-- 🔄 SWAP: ヒーロー写真 -->
    <div class="ph-img-box" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4c4ac, #baa88c);">HERO PHOTO<br>ここに写真を配置</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ PROBLEM ═══ -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="rv">
      <div class="sec-label">Problem</div>
      <h2 class="sec-title">こんなお悩みはありませんか？</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="prob-grid rv rv-d1">
      <div>
        <div class="prob-col-title">Brand</div>
        <div class="prob-row"><div class="prob-num">01</div><p class="prob-text">インフルエンサーを探したいが、自社で探すリソースがない</p></div>
        <div class="prob-row"><div class="prob-num">02</div><p class="prob-text">フォロワー数で選んだら、ブランドの雰囲気と合わなかった</p></div>
        <div class="prob-row"><div class="prob-num">03</div><p class="prob-text">大手代理店は最低予算が高く、月10〜50万規模だと相手にされない</p></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="prob-col-title">Creator</div>
        <div class="prob-row"><div class="prob-num">01</div><p class="prob-text">案件を探したいけど、事務所に入るほどではない</p></div>
        <div class="prob-row"><div class="prob-num">02</div><p class="prob-text">自分の世界観に合うブランドと仕事がしたい</p></div>
        <div class="prob-row"><div class="prob-num">03</div><p class="prob-text">発信力はあるのに、ブランドと繋がる手段がない</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 🔄 SWAP: コスメ・美容系の写真 -->
<div class="photo-strip rv">
  <div class="ph-img-box" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d8c8b0, #c0a888);">PHOTO — コスメ・美容イメージ</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ STRENGTH ═══ -->
<section class="sec-warm">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="rv">
      <div class="sec-label">Why Us</div>
      <h2 class="sec-title">コミュニティだからできる、<br>丁寧なマッチング。</h2>
      <p class="sec-lead">SELENE CREATORSは、仲介業者ではありません。自社ブランド「SELENE」の運営を通じて、クリエイターと日常的に関わり続けているコミュニティです。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="str-layout rv rv-d1">
      <div class="str-diagram">
        <div class="str-flow-step"><div class="str-dot"></div><div class="str-line"></div><div class="str-flow-label">SELENEのPR案件を依頼</div></div>
        <div class="str-arrow">↓</div>
